data.description: Almost brand new home close to Randolph Air Force Base ready for a new owner. Why wait to build when you can have a very gently lived in home right now? The current owners of this home chose many upgrades and have poured a lot of love and care into it. Three bedrooms, upgraded kitchen, flex space with custom built-ins, luxury vinyl plank floors in main areas, privacy in back and front and a short drive to so much! The solar panels offer a HUGE reduction in electricity costs and can be transferred to a new buyer with approval from the company. This home is ready to be yours!
